{"tid":276310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG 首發] 日本上網卡 Wifi 蛋 懶人包 (3)","createTime":"2017-06-08T17:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T17:10:24.000Z","uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80d00c78ecba5bc6ea298a44e8e20009d9768732","tid":276310,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:04:54.000Z","msg":"開到post 3.  你地有新既sim 卡用後報告的話, 請回報.  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你諗住起個post 係諗住問 &quot;我諗住去日本 XXX , 去Y 咁多日.  想問邊張抵用&quot;  的話</span>, 請睇左個Blog <a href=\"http://simegg.zerosaga.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsimegg.zerosaga.com%2F&d=x749Z7xx0Aspw3wVF5lTohv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5d3d310d\" target=\"_blank\">http://simegg.zerosaga.com/</a>  最頂寫住&quot;日本Sim 卡&quot; 個懶人包先.  懶人包都懶睇既話係無人會覆.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/4104/NbJczL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F4104%2FNbJczL.jpg&h=b721b44f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n個個去日本都實會買上網sim 卡.  為左方便眾巴打, 我寫左個Blog , 跟據係呢度個post d 巴打報既料, 分類唔同卡做左個總合. 每張卡一個討論, 可以係每張卡既post 報番你地既speedtest result.<br />\n<br />\n個blog 需要既係, 你地繼續報料, 因為只有用過賴過野既人報料, 下次先唔會再賴野. 好野亦都係要人報過出黎先知係好野.<br />\n<br />\n所以, 用完日本sim 卡或wifi 蛋, 記住影低 speedtest 既圖, 同做test 個地點.<br />\n<br />\nBlog 網站呢度. <a href=\"http://simegg.zerosaga.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsimegg.zerosaga.com&d=x749Z7xx0Aspw3wVF5lTohv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=83da657f\" target=\"_blank\">http://simegg.zerosaga.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭一個section 係General 點揀wifi 蛋同sim 卡.<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/7601/0pBSWc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F7601%2F0pBSWc.jpg&h=0a3ce58f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第2個section 係專講 日本Sim 卡. 一次出5張sim 卡介紹 , 多過5個post 有 Next 既掣跳下一版. 呢個section 全部都係講日本sim.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/4386/C4M2G5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F4386%2FC4M2G5.jpg&h=5a09fb49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第3個section 係講日本wifi 蛋. 如果多過5篇介紹wifi 蛋既post 既話, 都會有個Next 掣. 現時得5篇, 所以未有Next 個掣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/2483/Nhlvsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F2483%2FNhlvsn.jpg&h=16cce6a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第4個section 係講歐洲既sim 卡同Wifi 蛋. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/395/FVdldE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F395%2FFVdldE.jpg&h=400c3330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊post 如下<br />\n<br />\n1.  <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/65084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/65084/page/1</a><br />\n2.  <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/146048/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/146048/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f616d20ffeee72bbc0ff75b56a01c4b82664b40f","tid":276310,"uid":5339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6f752cfeb64a449fc3c0050dcf35aba406f119","tid":276310,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"依家我入完錢,恆生叫我入otp,跟住個網話failed fraud check,下面冇得揀8日4G plan點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\